ndlers/sandbox_delete.go` | Created | DELETE endpoint handlers |\n439: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go` | Created | Handler tests |\n440: | `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | Updated | Integrate lifecycle and GC |\n441: | `pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go` | Updated | Server integration tests |\n442: | `pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.go` | Updated | End-to-end deletion tests |\n443: | `pkg/workloadmanager/doc.go` | Updated | Package documentation |\n444: \n445: ---\n446: \n447: ## Notes\n448: \n449: - **Dependencies**: Builds on AR-004 (HTTP framework) and AR-005 (Sandbox creation)\n450: - **Store Interface**: ListExpiredSandboxes and ListInactiveSandboxes must be implemented by actual Store (Redis)\n451: - **Constants**: Uses values from defaults.go (TTL=8h, IdleTimeout=15m, GCInterval=2min, DeleteTimeout=30s)\n452: - **NotFound Handling**: K8s IsNotFound errors are treated as success (sandbox already deleted)\n453: - **GC Batch Size**: Limited to 16 per run to avoid overwhelming K8s API\n454: - **Timeouts**: All deletion operations have timeout protection\n455: - **Force Delete**: Available for stuck sandboxes with GracePeriodSeconds=0\n456: - **Stage ST-3**: Design complete, ready for implementation\n\n(End of file - total 456 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Store Interface Extensions\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Add `ListExpiredSandboxes` method to Store interface in `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`\n  - Signature: `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md","time":{"star