nnotation via `kubeClient.CoreV1().Pods().Update()` (delta-spec line 259-263, absent)\n5. **Test failures to fix:**\n   - `TestInformers_WaitForCacheSyncTimeout` (informers_test.go:75)\n   - `TestDeletionHandler_DeleteMissingSessionID` (sandbox_delete_test.go:134 — JSON unmarshal error)\n6. **Force delete finalizer removal** — delta-spec line 293-297, current implementation simplified\n7. **Documentation update** — `doc.go` missing lifecycle/gc sections (tasks.md T10.1-T10.3)\n8. **Validation checklist** — tasks.md Phase 9 items not fully verified (`golangci-lint`, godoc, coverage >80% for lifecycle/gc individually)\n9. **Integration with agentd** — idle cleanup coordination (design.md line 17, proposal.md line 67)\n10. **Mock store implementation** — tasks.md T1.3-T1.4 deferred, using `MemoryStore` directly in tests","time":{"start":1775846184163,"end":1775846184163}}}
